        <h3>Affordable Prices</h3>
        <p>We offer competitive pricing to suit every budget.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Easy Booking</h3>
        <p>Our platform ensures a seamless booking experience.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>24/7 Support</h3>
        <p>Get assistance whenever you need, wherever you are.</p>
